latestIgtvVideos.title: Easy five eyemakup looks tutorial
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hey Girls..! ♀️⠀
⠀
Easy five eyemakup looks tutorial (Full Video on IGTV)
⠀

First look : Apply any light color eyeshadow (i have used light brown) and some mascara

Second Look: If you love soft smokey eyes then this look is for you .. take first look as a bas and then smoke it out with dark brown eyeshadow 
Third look : Apply a concealor and make half crease and apply white eyeshadow and voila third look is ready

Fourth Look : Apply any golden color eyeshadow  on the half crease to create a illusion and fourth look is done

Fifth Look : if you are a winged eyeliner lover just like me then apply the liner and the fifth look is ready 
So this way u can create these five easy eyelooks and it doesnt require so many products.. Hope u like the tutorial  and Comment down below which look u like the most ❤

latestIgtvVideos.title: Soft Glam Look Tutorial
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Soft Glam Look Tutorial⠀⠀
⠀⠀
-Apply the moisturiser all over the face.⠀⠀
- Apply Primer to prep the base⠀⠀
- Now Take a orange corrector⠀⠀
- Correct the area under the eyes and around the mouth ⠀⠀
- Apply Foundation all over the face and blend evenly⠀⠀
- Apply concealer on the highlihhted points of your face⠀⠀
- Take Eyeshadow palatte and apply transistion shade above the crease⠀⠀
- Apply darker shade to create halo illusion⠀⠀
- Now blend both the shades ⠀⠀
- Apply mascara on the upper lashes⠀⠀
- Apply gel liner in the waterline⠀⠀
- Smudge the liner and blend evenly⠀⠀
- Now contour your face using contour powder⠀⠀
- Apply blush on apple of your cheeks⠀⠀
-Apply lipshade of your choice ⠀
- Its time to highlight the face and you are ready.! ⠀⠀
⠀⠀
Thanks for watching the video.⠀⠀
